title: The Rally
description:
The Rally brings an old school surf vibe to the compact cruiser experience. The design's mid-sized wheelbase and functional kicktail turns weaving in and out of thick pedestrian traffic and urban obstacles into the day's best line.

L: 33.25"
W: 8.50"
